          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/JuJuwalk/" class=" " title="JuJu">JuJu</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="14274905">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">整本书最让我醍醐灌顶的一句话：
&quot;Law can never make us as secure as we are when we do not need it.  Those freedoms which are neither challenged nor defined are the most secure.&quot;</span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/14274905/">(<span class="">24回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2011-08-26 04:42</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">57人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                整本书最让我醍醐灌顶的一句话：<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>&quot;Law can never make us as secure as we are when we do not need it.  Those freedoms which are neither challenged nor defined are the most secure.&quot;
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

